snippet.title: LAETUS. TRAILER 1
snippet.description:
LAETUS. is a rapid 2D precision platformer focused on speed and skill. You play as a small yet swift circle racing against the developer for the fastest time. Speed your way through 18 challenging levels and use all aspects of your movement and colour-changing abilities to finish in record time! (Hint: Intended ways aren't always the fastest...)

Releasing April 22, 2022 by independent developer AjSpeed.
